31
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:06,810
Ada lagi keseronokan akan datang.

32
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,530
Sayang sekali kalau terlepas.

33
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:09,590
Kenduri, ya?

34
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:11,810
Berhenti merepek yang bukan-bukan.

35
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,810
Adik saya berterus terang.

36
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,220
