00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,420
Di sini.

171
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:30,590
Qi Letian.

172
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:31,450
Di sini.

173
00:11:31,510 --> 00:11:32,570
Yong Lingchun.

174
00:11:33,510 --> 00:11:34,020
Di sini.

175
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,490
Yong Shiqiu.

176
00:11:36,350 --> 00:11:37,350
Di sini.

177
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:42,690
Pelajaran hari ini adalah tentang
jiwa dan manor jiwa.

178
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:46,610
The soul manor adalah tempat paling peribadi seseorang.

179
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,016
Ia mesti dijaga dengan baik.

180
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:51,210
Jika diceroboh,

181
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:53,810
ia bermaksud kematian atau kehancuran.

182
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:57,020
Tuan, bagaimana dengan rakan penanaman?

183
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,800
senyap!

184
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:02,940
Malah rakan penanaman

185
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:06,140
jangan mudah masuk manor jiwa masing-masing.

186
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:09,540
Ia amat berbahaya.

187
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:15,606
Jika anda benar-benar bernasib baik untuk mencari pasangan

188
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:18,140
yang berkongsi hidup dan mati dengan anda,

189
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:19,490
anda boleh mencubanya.

190
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,940
Tapi awak masih muda,

191
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,780
tidak sedar akan bahayanya.

192
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:28,900
Jangan mengejar kesenangan sesaat

193
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:30,850
dan kehilangan apa yang penting.

194
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:34,326
Terasa seperti saya dan Sima Jiao

195
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:36,610
